  "industry_note": "HfB₂ (Hafnium Diboride, hexagonal AlB₂-type) — Ultra-High Temperature Ceramic. Tm 3380°C, ρ 11.2 g/cc. σf 350-400 / E 480 / KIC 4.5 / Tmax 2300°C inert (oxidation 1700°C+ → HfO₂ 보호 layer). Thermal conductivity 105 W/m·K (가장 conductive UHTC). HfB₂-SiC composite (30% SiC) 은 oxidation 저항 boost. 항공 hypersonic leading edge, 군용 missile nose tip, 우주 RCS thruster nozzle insert. Hot-press 또는 SPS (Spark Plasma Sinter) 가공."
